    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 4. Damped Pendulum — Zero-Crossing Detection\n\nA damped pendulum:\n$$\\ddot{\\theta} + 2\\zeta\\omega_0\\,\\dot{\\theta} + \\omega_0^2\\sin\\theta = 0$$\n\nEvent: $\\theta = 0$ (each time the pendulum passes through the vertical).\nWe detect all zero-crossings and measure the decaying amplitude.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "omega0 : 2*float(%pi)$  /* natural frequency: 1 Hz */\nzeta : 0.05$             /* light damping */\n\ntspan4 : np_linspace(0.0, 10.0, 2000)$\n\n[traj4, events4] : np_cvode(\n    [w, -2*zeta*omega0*w - omega0^2*sin(th)],\n    [t, th, w], [float(%pi/4), 0.0], tspan4,\n    1e-12, 1e-12, adams, [th])$\n\nprintf(true, \"Zero crossings of theta:~%\")$\nfor ev in events4 do\n  printf(true, \"  t = ~,4f s, omega = ~,4f rad/s~%\",\n         first(ev), second(ev)[2])$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 18,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Zero crossings of theta:\no168  t = 0.2688 s, omega = -4.4271 rad/s\no168  t = 0.7836 s, omega = 3.7745 rad/s\no168  t = 1.2944 s, omega = -3.2202 rad/s\no168  t = 1.8023 s, omega = 2.7484 rad/s\no168  t = 2.3082 s, omega = -2.3465 rad/s\no168  t = 2.8126 s, omega = 2.0038 rad/s\no168  t = 3.3160 s, omega = -1.7115 rad/s\no168  t = 3.8186 s, omega = 1.4619 rad/s\no168  t = 4.3207 s, omega = -1.2489 rad/s\no168  t = 4.8224 s, omega = 1.0669 rad/s\no168  t = 5.3238 s, omega = -0.9116 rad/s\no168  t = 5.8250 s, omega = 0.7788 rad/s\no168  t = 6.3261 s, omega = -0.6654 rad/s\no168  t = 6.8270 s, omega = 0.5686 rad/s\no168  t = 7.3278 s, omega = -0.4858 rad/s\no168  t = 7.8286 s, omega = 0.4151 rad/s\no168  t = 8.3294 s, omega = -0.3547 rad/s\no168  t = 8.8301 s, omega = 0.3031 rad/s\no168  t = 9.3308 s, omega = -0.2590 rad/s\no168  t = 9.8314 s, omega = 0.2213 rad/s\no168$$\\mathbf{done}$$\nfalse"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "t4 : np_slice(traj4, all, 0)$\nth4 : np_slice(traj4, all, 1)$\n\nev_t4 : map(first, events4)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=1.5, name=\"theta(t)\",\n  lines(t4, th4),\n  color=\"#dc2626\", marker_size=6, name=\"zero crossings\",\n  points(ev_t4, makelist(0, i, 1, length(ev_t4))),\n  color=\"#9ca3af\", dash=\"dot\",\n  explicit(float(%pi/4) * exp(-zeta*omega0*t), t, 0, 10),\n  title=\"Damped Pendulum\",\n  xlabel=\"t (s)\", ylabel=\"theta (rad)\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 19,
      "outputs": [
        {
